@Bugzilla 112348 gmf_head anthonyh 051012 Sweep code for creation of Boolean objects
@
text
@/******************************************************************************
 * Copyright (c) 2002, 2005 IBM Corporation and others.
 * All rights reserved. This program and the accompanying materials
